HEADWORD: Bucket shop
<hw>Buck"et shop`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>An office or a place where
facilities are given for betting small sums on current prices of stocks,
petroleum, etc.</def> <mark>[Slang, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

